astra.text:
I am on a higher plane, Chale. Literally.
-# (chale: "friend")

Chaleeee! You are ready for this situation, right my friends?
-# (chale: "friend")
Now we show them, heh? They see our strength.
Okay! Okay guys! Let's get going. Win this.
My plan may sound irrational, only because you cannot see what I can.
Relax my friends. Time and space are... They're not what you think.
Don't underestimate me-oh. Gold is my heart and my soul cuts like the sword.
Waddup suckers! You okay?
Guys, don't think what you are fighting against. Consider what you are fighting for.
Five on five. We go clear them all.
We get the Spike down, that's one piece of the puzzle. Plenty more but one at a time!
No choice but to get that radianite, make we go.
That Spike they got is like a loose thread. We let them pull it, it's over, not today.

Them fools thought they get here fast? Huh. They must be running on Ghanaian time, cause chale, them late.
-# (chale: "friend")
Why would anyone agree to work in this cold place?

The secrets of this place, chaleee, they must wait a little longer. First, we fight.
-# (chale: "friend")
The world may be crambling, not this place-o, they thriving! Feel that energy!
I like flowers and stuff, but this place no give flavour. No gold, where's the signs, the bling-bling, come on!
As I myself predicted.
Yes! This is progress my friends.

Of course we won! Chale don't insult my personality.
-# (chale: "friend")

MVP me-oh, was this a dream-oh, chale give me pinch-oh.
-# (chale: "friend")
Don't mess with the guardians on their home turf.
I broke your mirror!

Hey, other Astra! If you know what I know, what are you doing? Yawa! Come on, clear off!
-# (yawa: "not cool")

Breach, you don't respect what you should. All shiny buttons, no juju.
-# (juju: "magic")
What up with that Breach? Ah! See him, kill him.
Take that boomer soldier boy out!
Bye-bye boomer!
This Brimstone got a space sattelite, heh? Ah, let's stick that yankee down into the Earth!
Okay like, I'm done playing nice with old yankee boy.
Okay Morocco, look alive.
Cypher, your head is too hard. I like you but expand your personality way.
Why, Cypher? Like you think I don't see you? I know who you are, man.
Fade! Woohoo! You are magical, girl!

This Fade's giving us nightmares, I got enough problems. Chale, for getting M’ako nɔ?
-# (chale, for getting m’ako nɔ?: "friend, am I guilty?")
Wash them away, water-boy.
Hey, water boy! You and me, let's show them how the scholars get it done.
Water-boy's making waves out there! Keep going my guy.
Why those relics chose this one. I'm never gonna know.

Chale, if my hair gets wet, you're in trouble, okay? Hey, I see that smile water-boy, don't even think it.
-# (chale: "friend")
How's the bling-bling water-boy? The ancient jewelry shines on you, no lie!
Daggers girl goes bye-bye.
Okay, robot-boy, I see you.

Their Kay/O's gonna mess with my power. Kwasia! Robot-boy is going down, that's a promise!
-# (kwasia: "idiot")
Killjoy-oh! The industrious leave a legacy!

Wassup, Killjoy? You and your little akokɔ crushed it.
-# (akokɔ: "chicken")
Let's make that Killjoy's toys look as dumb as her jacket, heh?
Neon, let's fly!
We got to bury that teleporting ghost.
I'm not sure what you are, Omen. But you did well.
Ghost-boy, bye-bye.
Check that Omen, okay? Ghost-boy is gonna try and sneak behind us, fam.
We get eyes on that Omen, then we bury that thing.
Simmer down, Babylon, follow me.
Not bad, Phoenix. Hope for you yet.

Ah, chale from Babylon! You good? You good.
-# (chale: "friend")

You dey bore me Phoenix. A warrior is known by his deeds, not his mouth.
-# (you dey bore me: "you're getting on my nerves")
Hey, Phoenix, chalk it to all this aggrandisement.
Raze, it's time to get cray-cray, my girl.
Yeah, Raze! That's my girl's boom style!
Hey, Raze. What up my queen? We could go show them how it's done, girl.
Raze, I love your boom style, my girl!
Let's take this Reyna down.
That creature is dead.
Waste that Reyna creature, end her.

Reyna, just stay in your lane, yawa girl.
-# (yawa: "not cool")
Waste that Reyna, guys. Before she beast mode.
Stay safe, Sage. I got you.
Drop that mystic healer!
Mad love, Sage. Come on, girl. That win's gotta be worth a smile.
Viper, don't get missing, girl.
Woah! Viper! You are fierce, gal!
I dropped your Viper!
Ah, Viper. What's your problem, girl? Who caused you such Rage?
I've told you, you are better than all this, Viper. Share your heart, heh?

Akoa wei paa ara.
-# ("look at this dude")
Too easy, too easy.
Better luck next life!
Enemy punished!
Nice!
Oooh. Come off.
I take them out.

Aboa!
-# ("animal")

Merekoo, bye bye!
-# (merekoo: "i'm going")

Kill am.
-# (am: "them")
Useless individual.
I killed them.
Just swag.
You dead.
Soul shots.
Boom!
I punish you.
Ah-ah! Idiot.
Serious, dead fool-oh!
Mmh-Mmh. Too stupid.

This thing, kwε, settled.
-# (kwε: "to see")

Ah! I end them. Feeli feeli.
-# (feeli feeli: "you have to see it with your own eyes")
I set the punishment on them.

Chale, I face one I kill him!
-# (chale: "friend")

No wahala, I end the trouble.
-# (wahala: "trouble")
And the enemy was punished.

I take lungulungu kill am eh... My own style wey I take kill am.
-# (lungulungu: "unpredictable/complicated", am: "them", wey: "okay/alright")
Trinity, you're welcome!
Quadraaa!
Quadra!
The barrel of the gun is always dark.
Look at my beauty.
No problem, no problem!
Ah! My gift to you and my lesson!
That moment is gone, but it'd be cool-oh. Now we are here, here.
You can tell a person's character by their first action. Check me then, heh?
We have plenty of time-oh, here and now. Be here and now.

I call you chale because it means you are my friend, but maybe I should call you kwasia cause you, you fool-oh!
-# (chale: "friend"), kwasia: "idiot")
Don't worry. Don't think it's heh?

No worries, chale. No worries.
-# (chale: "friend")
Have I told you you're okay? You're okay, fam. Good even.
My people are you ready? You must cultivate a sense of calm.
Take a breath now, release the tension. Good? Let's go.
I myself predict we will win. Again!
Yeaaah! Good efforts my friends.

Stand chale, stand tall.
-# (chale: "friend")
Ahah! We just do that again! Cool-oh!
Hey, that was audacious!
This is the continuation!
We are above this. We are above this.
Look down on them my friends.
Yes, fam. Yes. This is what we needed.
Now again! We must repeat that, our progress demands it.
I'm being truthful, that was good... And needed.
Gold is in our hearts, but empty your pockets, fools.

Equip yourselves-oh. Money dey falaa. Spend it.
-# (money dey falaa: "there's a lot of money")
This is the final moment of destiny.
We saw the beginning and the continuation. Now, the end.
We must be better now.
Rise up and hold.

Chale, like move from here.
-# (chale: "friend")
Oooh! Eternity blesses us.
Do not let yourselves fall.

Push forward, chale.
-# (chale: "friend")
Next time is now, fam.
Flow with this energy.

Yawa that, new energy now, heh?
-# (yawa that: "disgrace that")
Show me your true selves.
Alright, alright! Make me go, squad.
Be worthy, guys. Be worthy.
We are above them.
Let's make progress my friends. Make progress.
This is your glory.
I am with you, we are strong.
Rise and bring glory.
Woooo! Let's start.
Hey, people, come on now. I'm anticipating my congratulations.
Woohoo-hoo! I'm too sharp for them.
It was never in doubt. Yeah my people-oh, yeah.

Wo ntumi ntaake!
-# ("the enemy team cannot attack")
I myself know that was good! Walk majestically my friends.
Yeeees, my fam! This is how you prove yourselves worthy!
Beg. Try harder now.
It be so, everyone brought knives.
Pulling them in.
Blasting them.
Blasting 'em.
Knocking them.
Concussing 'em.
Blocking vision.
Obscuring vision.
Concealment.
World divided!
You are divided!
About there.
That'll work.
That should work.
Right there.
I got enough time to go into the astral form?
Brb fam, going to astral to do them astral guardian things I do.
Should I place some stars in this reality?
I should place some astral stars in this reality.
One second peeps, I gotta visit the astral to place some stars.
I should probably place some stars in the astral plane-oh. I should-oh.
Checking the situation.
Heading to the above.
Up I go.
Mmh. Let's see now.
Going astral guys.
I'm going above.
We defend this place-oh! Heh! We defend this reality.
Heh-yeah, it's good.
Defusing! I hope...
Come now, come on. Defuse. Defuse.
This interruptions. Ugh.
Okay, I'm still on it.
My ancestor say wassup!
Phew. Okay, nice.
Yes. That is it my fam. Phew.
Hey, too close. But close enough, heh?

breach.text: Stand in my way, I dare you.
These cowards aren't ready for me. No one ever is.
Guns in my face? Just another tuesday.
Nothing fancy, yeah? We go in, we crush them, we get out.
The faster we do this, the faster I get paid.
We treat this like any other job, no more, no less.
They're not intimidating, they're stupid. Big difference.
Been pulling jobs like this for years, risky? Sure. But never boring.
I don't need these arms to fight, but they're fun. Might as well use 'em.
You clowns brought me along, so we're doing this my way. Quick and violent.
Alpha Earth, Omega Earth, Kingdom... Who cares? Let's fight.
Don't get too cute with the plan, the more complicated our attack, the faster it goes to shit.
They're coming for us, huh? Sure. Their funeral.
Ah. Those idiots don't know what they're walking into. I'll rattle their heads, you take 'em out.
Look at this place! Kingdom has more money than they know what to do with. I wonder where they keep it.
Ah, LA! I've got a few spots I should revisit out here! Couple of foodtrucks, that bank in Malibu... Good times!
Hell yeah! Who's up for another?
Time to go home, scrape these bugs off my boots.
The fight is over? I just warmed up.
I always do the heavy lifting!
Maybe now you'll take me seriously.
Oooh! I've missed the cold. This was great!
I know. I'm great. You're welcome.
A second Breach? Huh? This might be a fair fight after all.
I hope you're ready, old man.
Brimstone! The corporate sellout! Here to look out for Kingdom's special interest?
Leave the fight for the rest of us, old man.
See? You're not too stubborn to die. You're just stubborn enough.
It could be worse, Brimstone! Instead of working together, we could be facing off! Or maybe you'd prefer that.
When that Brimstone sees me here, he's gonna be so pissed.
Hey, Brimmy. Remind me to play you this riff I recorded once we're done. I think it's a winner.
That Brimstone better stay out of my way.
Don't aim that camera at me, Cypher. Save it for the enemy.
Cypher, stop bugging my gear with microphones, you're worse than Interpol!
Hey, Deadlock, listen. What do you get when you cross 2 norwegians?
Well. Well. Well. Deadlock didn't screw it up. I'm proud of you.

Ska du föreställa en ståljeger?
-# ("are you supposed to be a steel hunter?")

Hey Deadlock, we make a decent team, eller hur? They attack and you butcher them, they stay put and I turn them to mush. Inte illa.
-# (eller hur: "right", inte illa: "not bad")
So, Harbor... Those relics you used to recover with REALM... You remember where they... Kept them?

I've got quite the payday coming my way, Iso. Tack-tack.
-# (tack-tack: "thanks a lot")
Damn, Jett. Have you ever considered a life of crime? I have contacts, let me know.
Killjoy, your inventions are too fragile! See these arms? Carbon steel with titanium plating! That's what you need.
So, the german has some fancy toys. Let's break them!
Omen! That scared the shit out of me!
Okay, Omen. I'll smash in the front door while you sneak in the back. It's a good plan, ya?
I'm gonna run my fist through that Omen's face. Can you even punch a ghost? Who cares? I'm doing it.
Phoenix keeps bringing the fire. It's like a viking funeral.
Let that Phoenix run his mouth, we'll shut him up soon enough.
You got fire in your eyes, Phoenix. I like that.

Mandou bem, Raze! How's that for pronunciation, huh?
-# (mandou bem: "nice job")
Raze! Together again and we're not even breaking the law!
Raze, don't wreck this place all on your own. Save some demo for me.
Reyna! I think I'm in love!
The enemy Sage thinks she will slow us down. That's cute.
That monk things she's an angel. Let's clip her wings.
Their Sage is a coward hiding behind walls. Grow a spine already.
That pretty boy Sova sure looks the hero, I'll give him that. I'll still kill him.
Just tell me where they are, Sova. I'll take it from there.
Viper, you're enjoying this a little too much.
It was never personal, Viper. Just business.
You never stop fighting, Viper. No matter what.
Quit your tip-toeing, they're all dead.
Kill everyone and our job gets a whole lot easier.
No one beats me, no one.
In a fair fight I'd still kill you.
What the hell were the rest of you doing?
I'll run through you every damn time.
Anyone else want to try me?
Never been in a knife fight, have you?
Time to take these arms for a spin.
They're not getting the message. Leave it to me, I'll rough them up.
If you're not being shot at, you're doing something wrong.
I'll do my job, you do yours.
Trust me, they'll know what hit 'em.
Are we doing this or what?
Come on, get me in the line of fire.
They think they're better than us, I can tell.
Just swapping-in new fusions cells. Okay! My arms are good, we can go.
I hate waiting, let's do this.
I've been itching for a fight.
You see an insect, you crush it.
They don't get to surrender, keep swinging.
They can run or get ran over, their choice.
This isn't a fight, it's stealing lunch money.
Their crew got sloppy, punish them.
The fools gave us a window, smash through it.
No point saving, spend it all.
Let's put them in the ground.
They want to fight? Let's fight.
Hit them fast, hit them hard.

Okay! Nu kör vi!
-# (nu kör vi: "let's go")
Is that the best you've got?
Hell yeah! Next drink's on me.
I could have left my arms at home.
I'm here to make money, not spend it.
I don't have to pack heavy, these arms are heavy enough.
Shut up and let me work.
Of course you still need me.

brimstone.text: They think I'm an old dog? Heh. I'll show 'em just how many tricks I know.
Failure is the great teacher. So let's teach 'em something.
No one die on me, we're all going home.
They can throw the whole play book at us, I've seen it all before.
I can't close the settings menu on my bracer. How do I? Oh. Got it.
Okay kids, we've got company. Pretend you all get along.
They've got one ugly looking crew. No offense to any of us.
Alright team! Let's go write this war story, shall we?
Let's ready up! We're here for radianite and we're not leaving until it's ours.
They picked the wrong day to mess with our world.
What did Kingdom get itself into this time?
I would hate to work in here. You couldn't pay me to sit at a desk.
Good work. Now let's evac this rock before it falls out of the sky.
Astra, help me manage the field. A bird's eye view is one thing then there's whatever the hell you got.
Don't let their Astra dictate our battle. Find the angle, take control.
That Breach is asking for it.
You did well, Breach. Don't expect a hug.
An enemy Breach? Ugh. There goes my good day.
Someone knock that Breach on his ass.
If any of you got a problem with me, take it out on my double.
That Brimstone is a stubborn ass. Hah. Reminds me of someone.
For a straight shooter, that Chamber sure can talk in circles.
So they got a Cypher? He'll see what we want him to see.
Jett, remember to stretch. I don't want you to sprain an ankle at 90 miles an hour.
Sorry, friend. Just doing my job.
There's something about you, Kay/O. Don't know what it is yet, but I like it.
Killjoy, I'm counting on that noggin'.
Killjoy, I say this with love but stay the hell away from my arm.
You left me no choice, kid.
Killjoy, do you control the admin account on my bracer? I might need you to reset the password.
Killjoy, control your bots, that turret keeps looking at me funny.
Let's roll, Neon! Show us what that K-Sec training did for ya!
Omen! You are a force of nature.
The enemy needs a good scare. Omen, you're up.
Human or not, that Omen can be killed.
Phoenix, if you keep pulling stunts like that, you can brag as much as you like.
That's how the boss does it.
I want to see heroes, not heroics. Looking at you, Phoenix.
We're fighting a Phoenix? Book your vacations now, this is gonna be exhausting.
Oh perfect, a hostile Raze. Kill her before she brings this whole place down on top of us.
It's open season on the enemy Reyna. If you get a shot at that heart, take it.
Let's kill that Reyna, our team has got soul, I wanna keep it that way.
Sage, if I die out there, you're in charge. Someone has to look out for these knuckleheads.
Sage, remember that you can't save everyone. We save who we can, that's enough.
Take us in, Skye. I want you on the front lines. Bring the whole damn zoo.
Sova, you look after yourself. You already lost an eye for us, one is enough.
Sova, we need eyes on the enemy. Tell us where they are.
They're the future, Sabine! You know you care about them.
Careful, Viper. You'll scare the kids.
Viper, watch those toxins this time. I'm not breathing in that crap again.
You want revenge, Viper? Now's your chance.
That poor Viper, we didn't have to be your enemy.
I like the way you think, we're overdue for a ride, aren't we?
Okay, time for a protein shake.
Sometimes you gotta get your hands dirty.
Stay in range of my stim beacon, we'll mow them down.
Who am I kidding? My knees are gonna kill after this.
Remember to talk to each other out there. If we communicate, we win.
Drink some water, reload your mags and let's get back out there.
I'll teach 'em to respect their elders.
My smokes can block the enemies line of sight, once they're blind, we move.
Shoot the bad guys. How's that for a plan?
Damn right we crushed it. Ugh... Even as I was saying it... When Jett says it... You know what forget it.
What do they think this is? A backyard scrimmage?
Keep taking this seriously, even if they aren't.
What are they doing over there? When the play is not working, call an audible.
Punch us in the teeth, we spit back blood.
Half time! Don't save a thing.
You've earned this win! Let's make it official.
The day is almost ours, take it!
Who do they think they are?
This ain't what signed up for.
That's why they put me in charge.
There's some things you just can't teach.
Any cheaper and it'll be just me and a bottle of scotch.
Not the boom you hoped for.

chamber.text: You have good taste my friend.
This killing is terrible business, but I always say: if I must do something, be the best.

Do not worry, with me this will be easy. C'est simple comme bonjour.
-# (c'est simple comme bonjour: "as simple as to say hello")
Okay, last looks. You all look wonderful? Me? I always look good. We are ready.
If you die today, I will remember you forever. It has been an honor.
None of this "a win is a win" nonsense. We should win big and look good doing it.
Ah! We've been noticed. Follow my lead, I know how to make an entrance.
I must say, I like what they have done with the place.
Which site shall we choose? I'll swing any way that feels good.
Our guests have arrived. Let's make a good first impression, shall we?
Oh no, invaders here to take our radianite. I'm sorry, let's go shoot them.
They actually think they can plant the spike? Impossible.
Be careful near the ship, that portal does not work as intended. Such a bad investment.
It is sad what happened here, such a terrible accident. One that I have nothing to do with.

A multiverse Nexus, enfin.
-# (enfin: "finally")
You were in my way, so this, was inevitable.
This was fun! We should do it again.

It has been a pleasure my friends! Au revoir!
-# (au revoir: "goodbye")
Goodbye, paradise. And good riddance.
I should go, before someone recognizes me.
Good luck Astra.
Let's see what their Astra can do.

Astra, what can I say? Je reste sans voix, I am speechless.
-# (je reste sans voix: "i am speechless")
Astra's gone.
Astra, it is delightful to see you. I'm at your service, mademoiselle.
Time to trust me, Brimstone!
Please, Brimstone. I am your key to the other side, you should at least pretend to like me.
No loose ends.

Au revoir frérot.
-# ("goodbye brother")
You knew not to trust me.
Oh, our deal? It's over. Sorry for the late notice.
Who is that well dressed man on the other side? Ah. The other me, of course.
Do not let my double shoot you. You will die.
So we have to kill my double? So be it.

Cypher, incroyable! You never cease to impress.
-# (incroyable: "incredible")
Cypher, I am sorry it has come to this.
Be careful with my secrets, Cypher. It is better, I think, if we stay friends.
Does that Cypher know how valuable his secrets are? I should be careful.
Tell me what you have learned Cypher. Oh sorry, I meant us. Please tell us.
Their Cypher knows too much.
They say efficiency is beauty and... Deadlock, you prove it.
Shut your demons, Fade. We all have a past, but it doesn't define us. One can only hope.
I never expected to be fighting ourselves, but we must embrace new experiences. Wouldn't you agree, Harbor?
Glad you can trust in a team again, Harbor. Let's get to work.
Handsome and a weapons connaisseur! Iso, you tempt me.
Kay/O, take them out.

Bien joué, Kay/O. You are unstoppable my friend.
-# (bien joué: "good job")
Toaster is broken!
I create weapons of war and I destroy them.
Kay/O, you are so industrial, it's a good look. But, if you need something more upscale, I have many ideas.
Do not worry my radiant friends, I will unplug their talking toaster.
Killjoy, I could never wear that jacket, but on you, superbe.
Terribly sorry, Neon. But you didn't like me anyway.
After you, Reyna.

Reyna, what you just did, je n'en reviens pas. I cannot believe it.
-# (je n'en reviens pas: "i cannot believe it")
Reyna, I must say how nice it is to work with you. It is so hard to find partners with your... Experience.

Did you all see Sova? Impressionnant, this man knows what he is doing.
-# (impressionnant: "impressive")
Sova, now here is a man of principle. But you have broken rules before, yes? Ah. Of course you have.
Viper, you must let me take you out some time. Dinner, dancing. I know the perfect place.
Viper, don't pretend you're not happy to see me. You're smiling on the inside, I know it.
And Viper, how are you? ... Ah. Sorry everyone, I have again left her speechless.

Beau travail, Yoru. You humble me.
-# (beau travail: "good job")
Bonjour, Yoru, your sunny demeanor is blinding as always.

Pardon, monsieur!
-# ("sorry sir")
Not your best.
Next.
One less.
So close.
Do better.
Too slow.
I don't think so.
You lose.
Away with you.
I win again.
So long!
That one's dead.
Terminus.

Aïe.
-# ("ouch")
I can't miss.
I'm a good shot.
I am sorry, we couldn't work out our differences.
It's a shame you had to die but you were not part of my bigger picture.
I would apologize to them but alas, they are dead.
Oh. I am not cleaning this up.
Okay, quick break.
Was that their best? How embarassing.
That's three.
And four!
Did you enjoy the show? Of course you did.
Oh, thank you, thank you. You are too kind.
I really am fantastic.

À votre santé!
-# ("cheers")
Embarassing.
Stand aside.
I'm sorry but I couldn't help myself.
It seems these strangers want me dead. Et bien, they are not the first.
Trust me, they will make mistakes, when they do, take advantage.
If you are not doing well, keep trying. We must keep up appearances.
Okay, which gun to pick this time.
One bullet per enemy, that should be enough, yes?
Weapon choice, it is so personal, non? You pick a gun and it tells me who you are.
Take aim, then fire. Let's not complicate it.
Let us see what they have planned for us this time.
These guns we use are okay but I will also bring my own. No offense.
These new friends of ours are not too friendly.
Please do not mistake my smile, I take this all very seriously.
I do like winning.
They reveal their weaknesses, not smart.
One step closer.
That was good. Another round, yes?
They are no match. Though I cannot say I am surprised.
Surely they can do better.
I thought I would have to work today. Clearly not.
This is just the beginning.

That was good but there is more to do. On est pas sorti de l'auberge.
-# (on est pas sorti de l'auberge: "we're not out of the inn/we're not out of the woods yet")
Now they are nervous.
Buy the best guns you can.
Spend everything. Don't be cheap.
Time to say goodbye.
This has gone long enough I think.
Kick them out.
Find a way through them.
Get them out of here.
Okay, start fresh.
I've done more with less. Keep fighting.
It feels like we've won already.
They should give up now.
Now, they have my attention.
Have a good time out there.
They are making this simple.
Keep your eye on target.
Let's dance.

Bonne chance mes amis.
-# ("good luck my friends")
Who will I spot first?
Focus now, eyes off me.
In we go.
How do I get away with these things?
Did everyone see that?
Did you see their faces? Sorry, I should not laugh.

Ce sera tout.
-# ("that'll be everything")
Bravo, you all did beautifully!
How did they think this would end?

Take their guns, vite!
-# (vite: "quick")
That's a good spot.
A gift.
That works.
I have them.
There they are.

Adieu.
-# ("farewell")

Parfait.
-# ("perfect")

Excusez-moi.
-# ("excuse me")
This should do.
Perfect.
All set up.
Farewell!
Away!
Goodbye.
They are so dead.
You want to play? Let's play.
This is too fun!
Oh-oh! I like it.
Oh-oh! I'm enjoying this.
Beautiful!
I love this gun.
They didn't actually think that would work?
No fireworks today, I'm afraid.
No one else could do this?
This is less than ideal.
Excuse-me, I'm working.
That was unpleasant.
Well, this suit is ruined.

clove.text: I've got all the time in the world.
You know what? If one of those lookalikes came over here and pretended to be one of ya. I'm not sure I'd be able to tell the difference.
Who's ready to die for this mission? I am! But you know, I'm cheating.
So are we gonna talk about the empty locker back at base? The one with the scratched out 08? Anyone? No one? Okay...
I know I can come back to life and all, but bullets still hurt, so don't get any bright ideas.

Look at this team! We're gonna kill it! And by "it" I mean those bams over there.
-# (bams: "foolish people")
Take 'em dead and alive. Probably dead. Well. Preferably dead.
Let me get this right, we're Earth's only defense and we still pay for our own weapons? Ridiculous...
Wait. Wait. Wait. I have a rock in my shoe. ... Nice. Free rock.
Have I been aging? Like at all? Still not sure how this whole living forever thing works.
It's fun being a secret agent and all. But I really hope that there's an alternate universe out there where I'm just growing old with a bunch of cats.
Ah. Radianite, we meet again.

Dinnae ken what they're on about? But I can promise them radianite will not solve their problems.
-# (dinnae ken: "i don't know")
What if set up some fake radianite? Imagine their faces when they unload a bunch of useless rocks.
Your party delves into the maw of the Earth. Jagged teeth of rock tower above you. A secret was stored here but no secret is kept forever.
Your party washes up on the shore of a deserted island. Strange experiments and even stranger phenomenom litter the sand.
Your party stumbles upon the rubble of a science experiment gone wrong. The souls of the dead wander the halls, it reeks of Kingdom.
Your party sets foot across a frigid expanse. Secrets long lost resurface through the shattered ice. The cold is relentless. Roll to avoid frostbite.
Your party arrives on the doorstep of a sun-soaked concrete jungle, the earth is brittle beneath your feet. You venture forth basked in gold.
We need to celebrate! Party in the danger room.
I hecking love this team!
And will do it again and again and a bunch of other times after that.
Don't let the portal hit you on the way out!
Stop their Breach before he stops us.
Bang.
That Chamber is dressed like a fancy waiter. let's ask him for the wine list.
Ooft. Not your best.
We could have ruled this world together.
Am nothing like the enemy Clove. I wouldn't be caught dead in that outfit.
Cy you wee punk! How did you pull that off? Keep it up.
Sorry not sorry.
You know we're a covert organisation. Shouldn't we be wearing masks? Cypher's got the right idea.
Wrap 'em up, Locky.
Okay, Deadlock, let's see more of that, aye?
No, my rules.
Fade mindgames are no match for my secret weapon... Ibuprofen.
Gekks! Do your thing!
Wings! How are you wee fella?
Wings! Dizzy! Thrash! Mosh! Youse are the actual best. Oh and, you too, Gekko.
You dafty.
Cya later Gekkonator.
Hey, Gekko. You ever think about teaching Wingman to use a gun? Just a thought. Write it down maybe.
Iso! Pull 'em apart!
Don't let their Iso separate us.
Iso! That was... That was beautiful!
Face the music!
So. Iso. You've got your own little pocket dimension, yeah? Hear me out. What if we threw a wee rave there. Think about it! Think about it.
Hey, Kay/O. My phone died on the way here. You think I could... You know. Can you charge batteries?
Watch our backs, KJ!
Just trip their Neon while she's running.
Boo!
So like those blue things on their Omen's face are eyes, right? So he has 3? Or is the middle one a mouth? Are they all mouths? COOL.
You plum.
You numpty.
Uh Oh. Me and Phoenix on the same team! They're gonna waste twice as many bullets trying to take us down!
Reyna. That was like a dance. A really violent dance.
The hunt's over.
Reyna! A certain someone tells me you play guitar, you have to play for us later. No getting out of it.
Reyna, the offer stands, take whatever life you need from me. She deserves it.
Well. Well. Well. They brought along my arch nemesis. Sage. Just kidding, we're like standard nemesis-ses-ses.
What! Skye? That was tidy! Is that. Is that what hiking does for you?
Skye, you're looking awfully braw today, could cut myself on those biceps.
Woah! Viper. You know what. I love your attitude.
Sorry snake-lady!
Hey, Yoru. Don't forget to fill out your character sheet again. You know how hard it is planning sessions around saving the world.
Yoru, how did you get so sneaky? Is it the hair? It is probably the hair.
Woah!
Pew pew!
Tidy!
You alright?
That's a kill.
Woah!
I shot somebody!
Have a kip!
Hi! Bye!
Target down!
Ha!
That's you, pal.
Skedaddle off.
No bother!
Down you go.
Sorted!
Critical hit!
Nae danger!
Nat 20!

Haud yer weescht.
-# ("shut up")
And That's another dead one.
I'll just let you think about that one, alright?
You did your best, just wasn't enough.
You made a mess of yourself.
Everyone has off days eh?
Don't get back up sweetheart.
That was their best? Huh? Alright.
That's three!
Four in the dirt!
Promise me you won't try that again.
And I did that with a sore tummy!
Please, please. Hold the applause until the end.
Aww. A wee shame, really.
You were only a moment, I am forever.
Fear me mortals!
Knock knock?
Surprise!
What? Did you not hear me?
Ah. Skill issue I'm afraid.
You know what we should do? I'll tell ya. We should win.
I reckon I'll take a kip after this. I've earned it.
Find the weakest link and kick 'em in the shin.
Don't be spending too many braincells figuring them out. Overthinking is just as bad as underthinkin'.
Youse don't get a reset button, so stay alive, please.
Listen up you muckers, if I don't get back up, just give me a nudge, I might not be dead, just taking a wee kip.
One downside to being immortal, I can't play dead.
Outside of this gig, immortability doesn't have as many day to day benefits as you think.
You know, I could just outlive them. Nah bullets are quicker.
Alright, lucky socks, don't fail me now.
Oh! This reminds me of this one time where I uh... Hm. Actually. Nevermind...
Alright, where to?
I can hear them hollering for their mammies from here.
Their tactics are... Unique... Uniquely not working for them.
The part where they lost was funny.
Alright then, some more of that and They're in the shite.
Simple and clean! Well done.
I reckon we're just better, aye?
Get a look at that! They lost again!
I feel bad for them. I really do. Just not enough to stop winning.
Now we start our winning streak of our own, aye?
Bet they are feeling frazzled.
They messed up, now we keep them down.
Last call for all the things we need to kill them with. Buy up!
I dinnae care how you do it, just spend all your money! Maybe buy a shorty or two.
It's been grand! But I've got places to avoid and people to ignore, so let's finish this thing.
They'll throw everything out as us, ya ken? Be ready.
Come on, friends. we're so close It's basically over.
Ah shite, I lost my pet rock!
Alright, muckers, off we go!
Roll for initiative.
I love this part!
Come on, then!
I'm here to stay.
I Don't quit.
Get on with it.
Guess They're fond of losing.
No stopping now.
I won't settle for a draw.
That's all they get.
I'll no lose to these bairns.
No more.
What about that winning stuff, aye?
Chin up, cuties, it's not over yet.
Push 'em back, They're stepping on us.
No whinging, we've come back from worse.
Look at 'em squirm.
Serious face, on.
Do I get a prize for that, or what?
Not today, not tomorrow, not EVER.
Brand new, that one!
There's a name for this? Oh yeah. Secondhand embarrassment.
Were they born yesterday or something?
We are just too good!
Just simple economics! I'm kidding. I'm terrible with money.
Refreshing!
Here, catch!
Have one of these!
Here, catch!
What a combo!
Saw that coming?
Ooo. Gotcha!
Feeling iffy, aye?
No peeking!
Dropping a smoke.
Dropping smokes.
No peeking!
Back like I never left!
You had your fun, my turn!
That was close.
Think I'll stay.
I'm back for good!
Fancy vacuum deactivated.
No radianite for you, wee man.
I'll see youse in a minute.
Well that's just grand.
I... I can't look, please don't blow up...
I'm just trying to do my job, here.
That was WEIRD.
Oof. I worked up an appetite on that one.
Ugh. Can I trade my powers in for invincibility? I'd much prefer that...
Just a wee flesh wound... I'll walk it off.

cypher.text: Nothing stays hidden from me, nothing.
They're scared. I don't need cameras to see that.
Nobody escapes me. But they'll try.
I wonder if they have any parts I can salvage. Mmh... Implants! I need those.
Ah, okay, this is good. I've got new gadgets to try out.
I must survive to protect my family. I can't lose them. I can't feel that pain again.
Let's see what I have to use. Pictures of their children? Wow. Way too dark.
I will stop anyone that tries to come through. I must keep my secrets with me.
The back alleys, or the streets of war. There is no difference, just nicer toys.
I'm prepared to die for this mission. Though I'd really rather not.

It's decided, their radianite belongs to us, you see? No ethical dilemma. Mesh moushkil.
-# (mesh moushkil: "not a problem")
Think of it this way. The more radianite we take from them, the less I borrow from all of you. Extra incentive.
I detect an incursion into our world. Ah! No! Laughs The other team is just very noisy.

These impostors threaten everything. Nora, mankdarch nkhelihom ikhesro lghzala diali.
-# (mankdarch nkhelihom ikhesro lghzala diali: "i can't let them destroy my little darling")
What has Kingdom done to this town? However pretty their lies are, they're just sucking my city dry.

Imagine all the information once kept here. Lost in seconds. Khsara.
-# (khsara: "what a loss")
Ah! I've always wanted to pry my way in here. Don't mind if I just leave some "gifts" behind.
Back to my workshop. Still much to be done.
Ah! So much learned this day, a victory! On many fronts.
Never come back, I will take you apart.
My truth stays hidden for one day more.
You're lucky I'm generous, or else your families would be next.
I knew your every move, it was sad watching you scamper.
I am PROMETHEUS and you are just a god.
Never come back, I will take you apart.
Get out of my city!
Breach breached.
Breach, Breach. I took a servo from your arms for my tripwire. Don't be angry. Breach.
Retire their Brimstone.
Let me see if I can hack into that Brimstone's bracer. If he's anything like our Brimstone, he won't know how to fix it.
Now where did Chamber build his nest?
With me, Chamber. Your eyes, my cameras. We make a good team.
Be mindful of their Chamber, he does not miss much.
Who will see better, Amir?
I'll crush your eyes, Amir.

Aywa bslama 3lik.
-# ("ok goodbye")
There can only be one.
I honestly don't know who the Cypher on their side is. Real mystery.
Who are you? Copy of me? Where did you come from?
Fade, leave their brains intact.
Fade, of all people, you've never asked to see my face.

Ahahah! Maalma! Who would have thought the nightmare lady would be so scary?
-# (maalma: "master/teacher" (compliment))
Now I can rest a little easier.
Ahah. Fade. Selam. I would offer you a camera, but your methods for gathering intel are a little less traditional.
Exercise caution around their Fade, not the type you want to meet in a dark alley.
Fade, keep those nightmares away from me. I already have bad dreams.
Fly my wind assassin, do what you do best.
No more running gal.
That wind girl is so jumpy! So annoying, my poor tripwires.
Let's go, little engineer.
Little engineer! I borrowed one of your transmitters for my camera. I'll pay you back. Probably.
Killjoy, do you have your soldering iron on you? I want it. I mean... I need it.
Goodbye to you and your secrets.
Omen, I have the information you asked for. But my price? My price hasn't been paid yet.
Go Phoenix, burn.
Phoenix, wow! You are really aggressive, I'm impressed! And a little scared...
Fire's out.
No rebirth for you.
Phoenix, our little star, keep that furnace burning, okay?
Blow them away, Raze.
Raze, you powder keg, nice work!
Ah, Raze! Don't tinker with my gadgets! I don't need exploding cameras again. The cleanup was so messy.
Reyna, jeez! Leave some for the rest of us. Or don't, I am sorry.
Reyna killed.
Remember everyone, she can only suck our souls after we die. What a charming woman.
Healer killed.
So, Sage, you can bring people back from the dead? Anyone? No constraints? Interesting.
Sage, keep me alive, I still have things to do.
I will kill their healer, it's the only way to keep them all dead.
Wait, wait, wait! Do I have the definition of hippie wrong? Because that certainly wasn't peaceful.
Let's blind their scout.
Sova, I accessed your background file. A good story, but that's not really how you lost your eye.
Ah, Sova! My mesured friend, that was amazing!
Between you and me, Sova, there's nowhere they can hide. How fun.
Their Sova will see what I want him to see.
You know, Viper, the name Sabine really fits you.
Viper, you're channeling that fury into real power. Keep it up.
Poison's gone.
Viper, whose birthday is March 20th? I found it when huh Okay, okay. I have everyone's passwords.
Their Viper's poison is not just physical, it's psychological as well. Keep strong.
Wow, you are cool! Like really. Are you even sweating?
Remember, the riftwalker is over there. Never think you're safe.
Goodbye.
Put down.
Ouch.
Enemy down.
Hostile removed.
One dead.
Buried.
One down.
Foolish.
No hard feelings.

T'hala.
-# ("take care")

Bslema.
-# ("with peace/goodbye")
Headshot.
My eyes are better than yours.
Erased.
Eagle eyed.
Deleted.
Trickshot.
Wiped clean.
Okay, time for a break.
Oops. No one to interrogate.
Squashed the last bug.
Okay, they're dead. Take what's useful.
I saw your secrets, they made you weak.
Three out of five.
Four out of five.
You're dead and I didn't feel anything, not even a thrill.
Ah, you forget. I've always been a killer.

Safi skot.
-# ("okay, shut up")
Knock knock.
You should have been looking more closely.
One of my cameras is broken! Oh wait. Okay, it's fine.
Where will they go this time?
They will scurry and then they will die.
I can't see them yet, but I can feel them getting ready.
Give me a moment, I need to set back up.
If they try something, I'll see it.
Remember, wipe the prints from your guns. It's just good crime scene etiquette.
Will they try the same old tricks?
They're usually distracted once I reveal them. Make sure you take advantage.
We know more than we did before. Let's use that.
I find them, I kill them, simple as that.
They're on the back foot, let's deliver another blow.
Find them again, kill them again.
Good work friends, keep using my vision to your advantage.
An injured dog bites hard, careful.
We're doing good. Let's do better. Just for fun.
Blink and they'll catch up. Stay alert.
Wonderful, it's great to see how frightened they are.

Their confidence beggins to crack. Anashouft. I can see it.
-# (anashouft: "i saw")
Let us use our sight to our advantage.
Don't worry, the house always wins.
Spend like there is no tomorrow, because there just might not be.
We lose our money after this. Might as well use it.
Nothing will be saved after this. Use it.
I saw their desperation. Let's use that.
Let's close up shop, I have things to do.
We must shore up our defenses!
I must weave my web better.
Let me find you again.
Don't get cozy.
That radianite must be ours.
We must keep them out.
My eyes will tip the balance.
I will find them.
They have nowhere to hide.
Let's knock them down.
My intel is their obstacle.
They crash against our wall.
I will find you.
Okay, let's get setup.
I will find you.
We will reveal their secrets.
Where are you?
Now, where to setup shop.

Yalla! Mcheena!
-# (yalla: "lets go", mcheena: "we're going")
You copies are nothing.
You forget, I always play high stakes.
You guys are so much better than my last team.
They were blind.
No one left to send a message? Oh well.
You think I don't know how to get by without money?
I'll try to even more poor, next time. It'll be hard, but I'll try.
Found you.
Caught one.
Careful now.
Cage triggered.
Now, let's see.
What can we see?
Here we go.
Got you.
Tagged.
Where is everyone hiding?
I know exactly where you are.
Give me a corpse.
That goes there.
Oh, this is a nice spot.
Yes, this should do.
This goes here.
You were probably afraid.
Only I could see you hide. Don't worry.
I saw you scurry.
Spike defused.
This is no problem.
Don't interrupt.
For a moment, I saw them.
Nora, I will see you again.
I hate visiting underground doctors.

deadlock.text: Trust me, we can get this job done.
The weight of our mission is upon us now.
The greatest battles ever fought are written in story books, may they write about this one.

Nanowire armed and ready. Kom igjen dere.
-# (kom igjen dere: "come on guys")

As long as I live, so does every ståljeger before me! To battle my sisters.
-# (ståljeger: "steel hunter")
Ammunition, time, life, these are all resources, spend them wisely.

Oh there's only five of them? Kjedelig.
-# (kjedelig: "boring")
Here again, we face our death. And again we will defy it.
Ready up, first we put them on their heels, then we put them in the ground.
Let them come, eagerness will endue them.
Oh the crisp air, the crunch of ice, reminds me of home.
Pack your bags, tally your kills, we're heading home.

Å fy faen! Well done!
-# (å fy faen: "oh damn")
Breach, shut up. If you were funny, I'd come to your open mic nights.
Not bad, Breach, a little messy but... Not bad.
Hi, Breach. Nothing too crazy this time, yeah? I prefer writing a simple mission report.

They brought Breach. Å herregud, I feel the headache already.
-# (å herregud: "oh my god")
Breach, between us, we have three very strong arms. Don't we?
Make no mistake, their Breach hides behind the chaos.

Jeg er lei for det. One of us had to fall.
-# (jeg er lei for det: "i'm sorry")
Leave Deadlock to me. I know how she thinks. I know her weaknesses.
Fade, now you're just showing off.
Fade, if you run short on nightmares, seek me out.I will gladly share mine.
Gekko, keep a tight leash on those creatures. For their sake.
That Gekko gambles his own life for those creatures, he couldn't make the hard choice. I will.
Neutralize the enemy Gekko and you neutralize his creatures.
Harbor, where the hell did you train?
Harbor can splash about all he wants, he won't shield them forever.
Technology at its finest, well done Kay/O.
Kay/O join me on the line, we do not flinch in the face of death.
But this is the most relaxed I've been all day.

Skye, you would have made a fine ståljeger.
-# (ståljeger: "steel hunter")
Skye, no matter where you start the fight, we finish it together.
Skye, don't get shot, I need my hiking buddy in tip-top shape.
Their Viper will try to separate us. Stay focused. Stay together.
And that was your best one, huh?
A jotun couldn't kill me. What chance did they have?
Try it again, the end will be the same.

There is no hiding from a ståljeger!
-# (ståljeger: "steel hunter")
Let me get that close and you're already dead.
Make them regret their choice of profession.
There's no need for the enemy to suffer. Kill them fast.
You're all more important than words on the brief. Look out for each other.

Vær forsiktig. The battlefield changes with every play.
-# (vær forsiktig: "be careful")
They think themselves are equals? They are mistaken.
Combat is a means to an end and WE are the means.
Add a tally to the board.
Remember what worked and test them again.
A momentary win, let us make it permanent.
I've taken walks more dangerous than this.
Okay, we're doing well, but keep focused. Adrenaline is a dangerous thing.
I was told this was a challenging mission.

Da var vi igjen midt i smørøyet. Good stuff.
-# (da var vi igjen midt i smørøyet: "again, we were in the right place at the right time")
Now they have a reason to be afraid.
Spend wisely or spend foolishly, just spend.
Buy the best gear before it's too late.
Careful now, their desperation will be dangerous.

Dritbra, that was good! Now we end this.
-# (dritbra: "shit")

Do they think we yield? Å nei da.
-# (å nei da: "oh no")

Kom igjen, cut them down.
-# (kom igjen: "come on")

Ut på tur aldri sur.
-# ("out and about, never pout")
I have seen death and I am not impressed.
I know how to fend for myself.

Jada! A-and you're all safe! Very good!
-# (jada: "yes")

Jeg prøvde ikke engang. Imagine if we had good weapons!
-# (jeg prøvde ikke engang: "i didn't even try")
I hear you, I catch you.

Det var nære på! All is well.
-# (det var nære på: "that was close")

Iselin, dette får du til.
-# ("you got this")

Hva i helvete? Where was I?
-# (hva i helvete: "what the hell")
I told you I would not die today.

I am keeping my grave empty, tusen takk.
-# (tusen takk: "thank you very much")

fade.text: Don't worry everyone, I won't tell them what scares you. Promise.
I paid a heavy price to commune with Nightmare. Don't waste it.
It doesn't matter where they hide, I'll find them. I always find them.
Oop! Eyes open, we have a job to do.
Another mission? Good. Anything to keep me awake.
There's truth in every dream, if you dig deep enough. Let's find out what they buried.
Let's cut them down then plant the spike and sweep the stragglers into the trash.
We find what's hidden, we take it, then we leave.
How many times must we turn them away? I'm getting aggravated.

They think they can steal from us? Hadi lan this is funny.
-# (hadi lan: "come on")
Many people died here. Their fear still lingers.
The nightmare is over. For them at least.
Okay, time for coffee, my treat.
We won, they lost. This is the way of things.
When in doubt, let the astral guardian do the job.
I chose to trust you, Brimstone. Show me I made the right choice.
So Chamber is more than just a nice suit? Well done.
Chamber, I mark them, you shoot them. It's a good arrangement.
Their Chamber is dangerous from afar, but up close, he bleeds like the rest of us.
So Clove. How exactly did you... You know. Become immortal.
There are more valuable secrets than the look of someone. Will you share those?

Helal Cypher, there is no hiding from you, is there?
-# (helal: "nice")
Their Cypher has a fear filled with regret. Voices calling for help and he cannot answer.
You have such a way with information, Cypher. After this, let's trade notes.
Leave the dream seer to me.
Sleep my sister, you've seen too much.
I admit, fighting beside a killer robot is a plus.
Kay/O, a radiant's nightmare. So glad we are very good friends.
Their Kay/O is tough. A bullet is tougher.
Omen, I wonder. How quickly can we unravel their will to fight?

Omen that gave me the chills abi, the good kind.
-# (abi: "bro")
Omen, with me. Nightmare thrives in the dark.
They brought along Omen. His fear is a sorrowful kind. Like a broken doll lost in the attic.
Talking a big game doesn't mean much if you lose.
Their Phoenix shines on the outside, but within, I feel his doubt.
Raze, you do not fear the chaos you inflict. I'm impressed.
Reyna, after you take from the fallen, what remains? It makes me wonder.
Mmh. That Reyna is not as fearless as she appears.
Together, Viper. Fear and toxin is an effective combination.
We must make the enemy afraid, look at Viper, yani. Scary mask, scary voice. She understands.
That Viper believes she's in control. She is not.
Did I get inside your head?
Don't worry, I did all the work.
And I didn't even need a gun.
Pry open their mind. Find the weakness.
Their teeth will chatter in the cold and dark.
Make their fear your weapon. Or use a gun. Whichever.

Boş yapmayin, keep fighting. Rest is overrated.
-# (boş yapmayin: "cut the crap")
They have courage. But no one is immune to fear.
Dreams are a funny thing, one little twist and it all turns dark.

Whatever happens, sakin. Don't panic. Trembling is bad for your aim.
-# (sakin: "calm")

Hadi! Again! Their fear is a track and the track is fresh.
-# (hadi: "come on")
Hesitation is for amateurs. Let's go.

Nice work, lan. All of you.
-# (lan: "dude")
Keep hitting them like that and this job is done.
Their heart rate just went up.
Savor the good dreams while you can.
Look at them. Pale and sweating. All good signs.
We could finish this with your eyes closed. But I wouldn't recommend it.

Güzel, we are doing very well.
-# (güzel: "nice")
You don't need nightmare powers to see them shaking.
You see? There's still plenty of fun to be had.
The nightmare turns in our favor.
This fight isn't over until we are dead.
Buy what you need, otherwise we are going to look very stupid.
Spend everything, hoarding money is useless now.
This is it. Their courage falters.
Their spirit is cracking, now shatter it.
Did they really think they could scare me?
Nothing's perfect, but that was perfection.
Next time we'll use wooden sticks. Make it fair.
Like a fly in a web.
Who are you? What do you want?
Push a button, save the day, easy.
You have got to be kidding me.
That's going to leave a scar.

gekko.text:
Wachale güey, my crew is coming through.
-# (wachale güey: "watch out dude")

Stealing our radianite is one thing, but I swear, if they touch my coffee mug collection, I will erase them from existence.

Meine Güte! How many spikes do they have anyway? That tech is not cheap.
-# (meine Güte; "my goodness")
If this town had let me install my defense matrix, we wouldn't have to be here. Oh well. I'll clean this up myself.

Alpha this, Omega that. Scheiße! Who named these universes? A und B would work perfectly well. We would be A, of course.
-# (scheiße: "shit")
I knew it would all work out, it always does.
Who's up for a debrief? Anyone? No one?
Okay everyone, take a test tube, thank you. Let's collect samples and get out of here.
My genius doesn't stop in the lab.
Okay, that's done. Time to lower this place.
Astra, after this, let's grab coffee and talk theoretical physics. Just us girls!
I will stop that Breach.
Breach, I wish you take my extra reactor coolant. Ugh. If your arms overheat out there, don't blame me.
Watch over us, Brimstone.
Brim, have you considered embedding your bracer in your limb? I can do that, you know.
Brimstone! That was wonderful!
Brimstone, remember, your screen isn't frozen. It's just locked. And no, the internet isn't down. It's never down.
It feels bad to kill that Brimstone. I mean I will, just, feels bad.
They brought along Chamber? I've seen his type before, overdresses and underdelivers.
Chamber? About that nanotech for your guns, do you like... Have any extra? Or...
Cypher, can you show me around the dark web one of these days?
I didn't realize we had 2 geniuses on the team!
Their eyes are down.
Cypher, my condensator cables are missing from the lab again. Put them back please. Thank you.
Cypher, your homemade gadgets are so cute! Reminds me of some of my work in kindergarten.
Cypher, let's keep sharing information. Every data point helps.
Let's go, buckethead!
Kay/O, you are the best! Now imagine if you let me install those ordnance mods. Huh...? Huh...? Come on!
Okay, he's off. Now where is the factory reset?
I'll show her who the real genius is.
My double's dead.
Heh! Looks like I was the smarter one.
I know that Killjoy's tricks. Wait! She knows mine. Ah! Finally, a challenge!
Neon how much power do you generate exactly? If I could just attach this meter.
I'll get that spooky ghost boy.
Be safe, Raze.
Okay, Raze, fine. Your tinkering may have made my tech better. Nice work.
Sorry little mouse.
Raze, I found a new album you just have to hear. Maybe you could... Come over after the mission? But only if we survive.
The enemy Raze's tech is just spare parts and duct tape. It's a wonder she hasn't blow herself up.
Drive them crazy, Raze. You're good at that.
Get them Reyna.
Reyna, I can see why you don't want any of my tech. You're scary enough without it.
Reyna killed.
It always feels like Reyna is after me personally. Does anyone else feel that way? No? Just me?
Sage killed.
Show us the way, Skye.
Skye, you are so cool and collected. I'm almost jealous.
Nature girl down.
Your creations were too primitive.
The enemy Skye is here, but don't worry. My robotics will beat her organics every time.
Okay, Skye. Get us to a good position then I'll lock it down.
Skye, with a few genetic modifications, your animal flora could be even stronger. Wait, was that offensive? Ugh. Sorry.
No more Sova.
They have Sova over there too? Can someone um... Steal his eye? What? I wanna see what's recorded.
Viper, I am speechless... And I always have something to say.
You stopped thinking clearly. This is for the best.
Viper? Do you mind if I run today's tests. You're... A little too biased. No offense.
There's a Viper over there. What a shame to rid the world of that mind. But I think she needs to rest.
That Viper is so hateful. How could she even think straight?
Look out for their riftwalker.
Uh, oh! The cool kid in class has some brains too! Impressive.
That rift boy is going to teleport himself right into one of my traps.
Terminated.
Good.

Auf wiedersehen.
-# ("goodbye")
That's done.
Goodbye.
Finished.
Enemy down.
One down.
Variable removed.
Got one.
Perfect accuracy.
Deleted.
Precise.
Impeccable kill.
Headshot.
Power's out.
You tried.
Who could have predicted this? Oh right, I did.
They're all dead? I have more tests to run!
Anticipated.
Let me just swipe those biometrics.
Is this their best?
Got three!
Now four!
Go ahead, call me tech support again!
Oh, okay.
Be smarter.
I have to keep it fun, you know.
I can hold an area pretty well myself. Make sure to cover the angles I can't.
Don't die. If you need help figuring out how, just ask.
Where are we going this time? Remember what worked in the past.
Their tech is only as good as their skill. And there, we have them beat.
Everyone makes fun of german efficiency. Haha. Just keep laughing as you use all my gear.
You can trust my bots. They only malfunctioned that one time and honestly she won't miss that finger.
Don't stress if I die, it was great knowing you all. Also delete my hard drive.
They look like us, but are they us? I have so many questions.
Everyone note down your observations then let's run it again.
Remember, your weapon is only a tool. You can't just shoot. You have to think.
Is everyone's tech still working? Double check it, please.
They are thinking so hard I can smell their circuits frying.
Good. One step closer to being back in pajamas.
Good. Analyse then improve.
They should probably reevaluate their approach.
I evaluated their strategy. It's a joke.
Let's see. Battles are won by geniuses and I am a genius. So...

I knew this would be easy but mein güte.

Oh this is a much better trajectory.
Their stale tactics would only work for so long.
Last round to use our creds and abilities. Don't waste your firepower.
Oh, almost done? Cool. Cool cool cool.
Once we win just dump all your tech in my lab, I'll fix it up.
We can keep them out.
I anticipated us winning.
We are not their equal.
Their defense? Um... Could be better.
Just cool down, we're good enough to win.
Find the leverage and wedge it open.
Nice and easy.
Reevaluate tactics.
Keep your heads on.
Keep doing what you do best.
We can't keep doing the same things.
Tactic beat firepower. Use that.
Quick picks now.
Time for a field test.
Keep it cool, that's how you survive.
Don't overthink it, that's my job.

Calculated.

Like clockwork.

Swarm grenade out.
Placing swarm grenade.
Placing alarmbot.
Alarmbot out.

Placing sentry.

Initiated!
You should run.
Got them ALL!
Area's clear!
Caught one!
Caught two!
Caught three!

Caught five!
Fish in a barrel.

Had some trouble?
Bot coming back.
Recalling my bot.
Bot assist.
Tag teamed.
Thanks, bot.
Allie, oop.
Love my bots.
Thanks, bottie.
Oh. No no. You don't deserve my inventions.
Imagine if I died right now. So funny.
Don't. Interrupt. My work.

Phew. Heiliger Strohsack, this is crazy.

neon.text: Radiant powers, deadly tech. I'm sure we won't break anything.
Let's go! World's not saving itself.
Another site on the brink of destruction. At least we're consistent.
Look, I'm glad you're all here. There, I said it.
Enemies in our way? Hope they like getting hit by lightning.
This covert-ops thing, I kinda of like it. Let's not mess that up.
Any chance they'll let us through? Fine, we'll do it the hard way.
Here's the plan, whatever they got, tear it down.
They come at us, we push them back. They don't stop, we don't either.
Huh. They came all this way. That was stupid.
Big surprise! Someone blew the fuse. No wonder you brought me.
What did I say? Don't mess with me.

Ayos! That's how we do it.
-# (ayos: "nice")
For their sake, I'm glad it's over.
Oy, Astra! How would I, hypothetically, go to other worlds or whatever?

Astra, your aim was on point. Husay.
-# (husay: "well done")
Chamber, I'm here to fight. Whatever you are scheming, leave me out of it.
Don't listen to that Chamber. What he wants is not what he says.
Clove? You were up at 3AM watching cooking videos, how are you awake right now?

Hanep, Cypher. Hope you caught all that on camera.
-# (hanep: "damn")

Cypher, get their good side. We don't want to be rude.
Enough cameras, their Cypher's gotta go.
Gekko, you told me you'd buy me boba later, I'll hold you to it.
Jett wins again! I am shocked.
Save it, Jett. I'm not racing you. You'd only embarrass yourself.
Fair winds, tight corners, time to show-off, Jett.
That Jett is all speed no skill, she's mine.
Killjoy, my suit's got like a billion volts. Don't touch it.
That's my double, yeah? I got her.
My double thinks she can take me? Bad call.

Hoy, Raze. Raze! Dibale na!
-# (hoy: "hey", dibale na: "never mind")
So, Raze, you got a plan? Or you're gonna... You know... Do what you always do.
Raze, the plan is... Nevermind. Just keep blowing them up.
You and me Reyna, no limits!
Reyna, remind me to never piss you off.
That Reyna won't hold back. I won't either.
I'm ready, Sage. We got this.

Galing mo, Sage. I gotta take notes.
-# (galing mo: "you're awesome")

Skye, I like morning runs. But morning implies sunlight. No more 4AM wake-ups, you maniac.
Skye, if your pets find them, tell me. I don't speak wolf or tiger... Whatever...
That Yoru looks pissed all the time. Honestly, it's impressive.

Tapos kana! You're done!
-# (tapos kana: "that's it")

That was their best, diba? Not impressed.
-# (diba: "right")
You made me care. Big mistake.
All done. Please, don't hug me.
Please stay alive. I hate making new friends.
Listen up! Kill them before they kill us.

Hoy! Fight's not over you know.
-# (hoy: "hey")

Ingat ka. Don't get stabbed. Bad way to go.
-# (ingat ka: "be careful")
Fight 'til the end. No matter what.

Tara na! Clock's ticking.

They'll hit back, or at least they should.
Fine, I admit it, that was nice.
Free target practice! I'll take it!
I belong here. We all belong here.

My Lola was right, weeds are difficult to kill.
-# (lola: "grandma")
Spend your cash, don't look back.
No point saving, buy it all.
We can all agree losing sucks. Come on, let's win.

I'll show them. Lintik kayo.
-# (lintik kayo: "get struck by lightning")
Get these losers out of here.
Whatever they're doing, I like it.
Could be worse. Could be better.
Switch it up? Just for fun.

Tabla tayo, I'd rather win.
-# (tabla tayo: "we're tied")

Halika na! We can do this.
-# (halika na: "come on")
Kick them out. I don't do visitors.
Try that again, I dare you.
We crushed it! Should we... Celebrate or something?

We did that. Lola, I know you'd be proud.
-# (lola: "grandma")
That was clean, keep it up.
I've tried explosions, not a fan.
I didn't come here to die.
Are you kidding me right now?

omen.text: I am the beginning, I am the end.
Do they know what it means to be truly afraid? I'll show them.
How many must I kill before I am restored? More. Always more.
If I must live in this nightmare, my enemies might as well join me.
They fear death, they should fear so much more than that.
Make the right choice, even if it calls for sacrifice.
Who will they cry for once they know they are going to die?
I already feel their hope dying and we haven't even begun. This will not take long.
Wherever I go, obliteration follows. It is my legacy.
You've brought your monster for monstruous work. Fitting.
Do not let them plant that spike! Radianite explosions are... Complicated.
The enemy brought a spike. Kill them.
Millennia of Radiant history stolen from the world and crammed into this cave. How did I not see the wrong in this?
We should have left this place buried, nothing good will come of our meddling.
Is that... A statue of me? This is... Unexpected.
Split. Ahhh... They don't know the meaning of the word.
Rest now. I will keep watch.
Hold on to this moment, we can't stop here.
You thought you could escape my nightmare?
The Astra is gone and her mysteries with her.
Astra, your power sends shimmers through the veil. It is mesmerizing. Can no one else see them? Pity.
Kill their leader and the rest will flee like rats.
I told you, Chamber, I cannot eat your cooking.
Hey, mandatory break for you, Clove.
Their Clove is fearless in the face of death. I will show them a fate far worse.
Their Clove returns from death yet natural balance is preserved. How is that possible?
Do you see under my hood, Cypher? Does it scare you?
With you and I in concert, immediately.
Fade, that was a work of art.
They have brought Fade. Her consciousness is strained as my own. This will be interesting.
Together Fade, we will show them the true meaning of fear.
That Fade spreads terror well. Let me give her a dose of her own medicine.
Your combat precision, Harbor, I swear I've seen it before. A past life, maybe.
That relic won't work for just anyone, Harbor. Why you? Curious.
Iso, take them one by one.
I remember that it always ended in death.
Remarkable, your precision knows no bounds, Iso.
Their Iso buried hundreds, let us not be part of that statistic.
Iso I owe you a great debt. Um. Would you be... opposed to receiving a hand knit sweater?
Jett, you were a storm. Well done.
I will get inside their inventor's head, even brilliant minds will break to madness.
How many truths has their Omen uncovered? Whatever he knows, it will be mine.
I'll kill that Omen, I'll take his memories. I will remember.
I will snuff out Phoenix's fire.
There is a Raze, I sense her laughter. To laugh again...
That was incredible, Reyna. And they call me the monster.
Reyna, the souls you consume, do you hear their voices as I do?
The enemy fears you, Reyna. You can use that.
A radiant healer is with them. I can feel her pull against the natural balance.
Sage, the life you give, do you ever wonder where it's taken from?
Keep hunting them down, their Sage cannot protect them all.
Well done, Skye. Nature's wrath indeed.
What would you have become, Skye? Mmh... It doesn't matter now.
Skye, the lifeweaver, the power to create, destroy. Which path will you embrace, I wonder.
Oh, there is a terrible beast inside you, Skye. Unleash it.
There is a fury in you, Sova. It is terrible, beautiful.
Their Sova thinks himself a hunter, what will he do when he feels me closing in?
Impressive, Sabine. You always knew how to turn the tables on an enemy.
That I kill you now after all this time... Ironic.
I've made my peace with our Viper, I cannot say the same for theirs. She will learn to fear me.
Don't die here, Sabine. I need your secrets.
Sabine, look at the monsters we've become. At least, you have flesh to hide your horror.
You can relax, Sabine. I gain nothing from killing you now. Attend to the present, not the past.
Just think, Sabine. You used to heal with your skill. Funny.
Ordered to kill Sabine again. Does nothing ever change?
Anything can be made a weapon but I am sorry, I don't recall.
Freed from your prison at last.
There are no match for you, riftwalker. Not even close.
I'm curious, riftwalker, when you travel, can you feel the pieces you leave behind?
Where should we go riftwalker? They cannot watch everywhere at once.
You thought you could escape my nightmare?
I'll make them remember they're only human.
They think they know pain? They can't begin to comprehend it.
Strike at their weak points. If one link breaks, the rest will follow.
I feel the strain. Block it out, Omen.
Their backs will be towards at least one of us.
Look for my shadows, they will hide you.
I survived obliteration, I will survive them.
Wait until I blind them to strike.
I will take back what is mine.
I can feel their panic rising. Drive it into them.
Sad fools standing in our way.
Keep yourself together, you can't fall apart now.
I feel like myself, catch them, again.
I know how this will end.
I am not just a shadow.
I will rip the light from them.
Pity the man who dies meaningless.
I let go for a second.
You think you can kill me?

phoenix.text: Just take a seat. I got this.
Keep a healthy distance, I burn hot.
Don't worry guys, they say I'm a prodigy. Not my words, not my words, baby.
Let's make this quick, bro. I got things to do.
Yes, yes. It's me, autographs if we survive, yeah?
Relax, settle down, I got this and I'm not leaving until we're done out here, yeah?
When I'm done, there'll be nothing more than ash.
Okay, fam. If any of you die, I'll be vexed, so just keep alive, yeah?
All of this for some radianite. It's mad. Let's get it and be done.
Yo, let's stop these guys. For real. No one gets past me again.
Man, this weather is not on. Anyone got a jacket?
Really? You dragged your fire guy underwater? Fam' you're killing me.
Aw man, I was just getting warmed up.
They're done? I was just getting started.
Aaaah. Come on bruv. Like it was gonna happen any other way.
They're done! Who's up next?
And that's how it gets done.
Aaaah. Come on bruv. Like it was gonna happen any other way.
They're done? I was just getting started.
Okay, we out. Gonna go crawl under some blankets now.
Hey! And we didn't even break the glass! Double win, baby!
Oh! Astra with the galaxy brain, yeah!
Who's hungry? Astra, let's finish up then get Jollof. I bought last time, so your treat.
Astra, I bring the fire, you bring the stars. They are stars, right? Are they stars?
Tear them down, Breach.
Breach! You flash, I flash, everyone's blinded. Let's go.
I'm fire, you're Brimstone, let's go.
Looks like the old dog still got some bite.
Brimstone out.
Yo Brim, don't go tweaking your back out there. Leave the fancy stuff to the youngens.
Chamber! I'm ready for some custom guns. You hook me up, yeah?
Stop snooping.
Remember, fam. Winning takes sacrifice. Right, Cypher? Sacrifice? Like chess? Our chess game? Come on, I know you got it.
Cypher, thanks for setting your stuff up. It's super useful, man.
I'm feeling myself, today, Harbor! Bet we clean them up in twenty minutes.
I'll clip that Jett's wings.
Aw. Don't be like that. You know you'd also want my shoes.
You're mad, Jett. Damn.
Sorry Jett.
They've got a Jett too? Nah. There's only one wind girl and she's ours. That's a fake.
Come on, Jett. Me and you, we never lose. Let's do this.
Kay/O! Team Forge, let's go!
Hey KJ, you good with the tech stuff? Need anything, you know, superheated?
Tech support with the carry! Nice work.
Engineer's down.
Hey Omen, I respect a guy who knits. That's pretty cute.
Omen, you're not even winded! You sure you're human?
Omen wins by fear, don't let him get to you.
Gonna burn you up, Phoenix.
You're nothing cuz.
You should see your face.
Who's this other Phoenix guy? Nah mate, you are mine.
There can only be one Phoenix. I'm coming for you.
Aw. It's a shame I gotta take out their Raze. That girl is a one woman party.
Raze, plug me into the tunes, yah? I know you've got the good stuff.
Look out for that Raze, fam. Can't have you blowing up.
I'll crush her radiant heart.
Damn! That was impressive. Mexico in the house.
Damn! That was impressive. Mexico represent.
Reyna's down.
Hey Reyna, how old are you? No shade, you look great! But like, sometimes you say the strangest things.
Man, that malice coming off their Reyna. Feels like she's already hunting me.
Yo doc, keep us topped up!
Everyone just learned what I already knew. You're wild Sage.
Healer's down.
Easy, Sage.
Glad you're here, Sage. With you we can't lose.
Their healer is nothing, I'll burn them faster than they can mend.
Don't wanna take you out Sage, but, I gotta.
Guide us in, Skye.
You're mine, Sova.
Hey Sova! We're gonna hit the chessboard after this, yeah?
Scout's down.
Yo Sova, that owl's pretty dope. Would look a lot better with flames decals on it, right?

Yoru, let's see what you got, mate.
Okay, Yoru. Right here, right now. We'll see who's the better shot.
Riftwalker's out.
You go girl!

I'll outshine all their radiants.

Wha?
Skrrr!
Embarrassing.
Sorry bro!
Dead!
Target down.
You're out.
That's done.
Put down!
They're super dead.
Sit down.
Look sharp.
Walk it off, G.

What you doing?

Easy mate, there can only be one hero.

Uh... I can't see your guy.
Triple baby.
Quadra!

You thought you could come against I.
Pay attention.
Really?
Oooh...

Remember, stay out the fire, super-high level tactic, remember that, yeah?
I'm twitchy here, let's go already.
Look, don't start resting, still work to do.
Buy stuff, ka-ching, go skrrr, then we're done, yeah?

New fight, new tactics. Keep it fresh, yeah?
You man ready for a light show?

Y'all better keep up.
Feels good to stretch my wings.
That was easy!
They're still fighting? After seeing what we can do? Not wise.
Do they still want it? Mad guys.
I'm kinda feeling myself right now. Y'all better keep up.
Heeeey! I like this game.
Damn, this is fun. Let's keep it going.
Who else is having a great time? Just me. Aww. I'm gutted.
Knock me down, I'll get right back up.
Oh okay, we back in it now.
They're in for a rude awakening.
Either spend all your money, or give it to me. Good cause either way.
Spend it now or it's gone.
We win this battle, we win this war. Let's do it.
We win this battle, we win this war. Let's do it.
We got it this time.
Let's push 'em out.
Let's keep it rolling.
KEEP IT HOT!
Stop them! This is our turf.
Knock 'em down.
Gotta plug those holes guys.
Let's get the advantage.
They're not gonna get an inch.
Bring it up.
They should stop tryin'.
Let's turn this around, squad.
Let me show you how the boss does it.
I got you bruv.
Don't hold back.
Let's go!

Oh you thought you put up a fight?

You get that on camera?

All I need are these hands and this fire.
Going up.
Careful now.
Watch your eyes!
Flash!
Come on, let's go!
Jokes over, you're dead!
We good, we good.
All good, all good.
All good.
Cheeky.

You think you can kill me?

Vamos, Breach! Let's go!
