How did I get this powerful?
Night!
Didn't think I was that quiet!
Well that's a knife.
If you see one of my creatures, it's a good thing, alright? You'll figure out what they do eventually.

Just some good old hard yakka standing in between us and victory.
-# (yakka: "work")
Make sure to follow my pack in, they'll lead us right to the enemy.
These parasites aren't gonna take one step past this place.
I feel something over there. Can't place it. Like us, but... Different.
Another fight? Clean slate. Let's leave whatever happened in the past.
We know what we're doing. Trust each other and we'll be fine.
We move as a unit, okay? Last thing I need is some hero messing things up.
Don't sit down, we're not done yet.
I'm no doctor, but I can patch a bullet hole or two. Let me know if you need healing.

No wukkas, mate. Just keep it up.
-# (wukkas: "problem")
Keep that focus. More of that and we're out of here.
Keep that fire, yeah?
That's a good run.
Stay keen. They don't have to be good to be dangerous.
We're going off like a cut snake.
Well, I reckon moral is gonna be pretty low over there.
Now we're on the right path. Let's keep going.
There's the toehold, now just dig in and climb up.
They think they put us in the dirt. They're gonna find out we weren't buried. Just planted.
Don't save anything. Last chance to use our stuff.
One more, then first shouts on me.
Come on, squad. Gotta play that whistle.
We're not equals. Let's go.
Shut and lock the door.
Let's get this win.
Pull your socks up.
They can't get an inch.
Trample them.
Don't let me down now, yeah?
Let's go for the throat.
Keep them out.
Push them out.
Don't give them ground.
I got you, okay?
Time to mobilize my pack.
Find the weak point and break it.
Ah. Now there's some serenity.
Don't even try me.
In the words of our Sova, the pack, survives.
Now this is a team. You see that?
You beauts, that's what I like to see.
I'll crabwalk next time, make it easier for ya.
Healing over here.
Heal up, squad.
Time to hunt.
They're concussed.
Got 'em.
Ah. Wild.
Good boy.
Blinding.
Hawk out.
Good bird.
Blinded.
Seek them out.
I've got your trail.
Found one.
3 for 3!
There's another.
Don't even start that shit here, mate.
Why did I sign up for this shit?
Nice try, mate.
Wait. This feels different.
Shit, I'm buggered.

sova.text: Wherever they run, I will find them.
There is no retreat, not when annihilation is at stake. This is our day.
Don't be afraid, I've gone through rifts before.
I believe in all of you like I believe in myself.
This bow has taken man and beast alike. I found there is little difference.
I was told you were all the best, that is why I'm here.
You'll have your intel, I promise.
You have me, that is good for you.
Another day, another battle. So be it. I do not fear blood on my hands.
We will not withdraw until their radianite is ours.
Remember, the enemy defends this world. It is their home and that makes them dangerous.
Anyone that lays a hand on our radianite may find a bullet in their jaw.
As long as there is breath in your lungs, you have the strength to fight. Hold them back.
I am not tired, are you?
Today is not our day to die.
A little recognition is nice now and then, thank you.

My бабушка told me not to brag, but for this I make an exception.
-# (бабушка: "grandmother")
You were nothing compared to the alpha.
Good thing I was with you, yes?
The snow should hide our tracks. We were never here.
Stop their Breach at all costs.
Breach, we can only follow up if you wait for us. Nothing comes from rushing.
Their Breach has no patience at all. He attacks fast, be ready to move.
Brimstone, you are a true leader.
Brimstone, after we win, I'll buy you a drink if you share a memory with us.
Chamber, you are a good shot, but when you can bounce your bullets off the wall, then I'll be impressed.
Okay, Cypher. I admit, that was good.
Goodbye, Cypher. You will not be missed.
You've buried your secrets well, Cypher. But I am a hunter and I will find them.
Take out Cypher's cameras. He's weak when he's blind.
Fade, well fought, there is no other hunter quite like you.
The hunt doesn't always go as planned. Does it?
Fade, with you and I on the field, the enemies' plan will crumble.
The enemy Fade will use our fear against us. So it is better to be fearless, I think.
The monsters that Fade commands are imitations at best. She does not frighten me.
Their Jett is fast, so are rabbits and squirrels. I hunt both.
May the wind guide your blades, Jett. And my arrows.
Listen for the wind, it will tell you where their Jett is.
Killjoy is no threat without her toys. Break them and remove her.
Neon, perhaps I will nock an arrow in advance. There is very little time to react once you start the fight.
Thank you, Omen. Startled prey is easier to hunt.
Omen, we will find your answer. You will not be this way forever, I promise.
Don't forget who you are, Omen. A man, not a monster.
It is difficult tracking their Omen, but not impossible. I can do it.
You lack the patience, friend. Learn that first, then we'll approach strategy.

вот это да, no one can beat our Phoenix.
-# (вот это да: "wow")
In the wild, fire means life. You'll be our fire, Phoenix.
Raze, you always work to lift our spirit. Thank you.
Their Reyna prepares on the other side. Kill her before she becomes monstruous.
I did not expect a healer to fight so well. You are incredible.
Sova, I spared you when we first met. I can't let you go again.
I must kill my reflection, it's the only way forward.
Viper, for a scientist you are very violent.
Your justice frightens me, Viper. Is there no other way to find peace?
I will put their Viper down. It is mercy.
I survived much worse than you.
No one escapes my sight, no one.
I'm not just an archer, you know.
A bow and arrow is old fashionned. But sometimes old ways are best.
If you're not a good shot today, don't worry. There are other ways to be useful.
What do you say, drone? Ready to stretch your wings?
Stay taut as a bow string. The fight demands it.
Level heads until we're home, yes? Good.
We are strong because we are together. Don't forget that.
They demand a fight. Who are we to disobey?
Watch them run when lit by my sonar, that's when we strike.
Act on my intel. Don't give them time to reposition.
I have more than they have ever seen.
If we go easy on them, they will never learn.
Why are they so determined to die?
A second wind, let your senses come alive.
They aren't impervious. We can do this.
The winds shift in our favor.
We can end it now. Once more.
Their winter has come. Bury them.
Good thing I was with you, yes?

My бабушка told me not to brag, but for this I'll make an exception.
-# (бабушка: "grandmother")
They should have dug a deeper grave.

tejo.text: You know? I had a dream last night. We killed all of them and none of us died, I take it as a sign.
My father used to say: "The fight is won before the first punch is thrown." We've trained. We are ready. And now, we win.
Dropships, artillery, SOPs, just your typical retirement.

This is not a little game of banquitas. Focus or we carry you home in a bodybag.
-# (banquitas: "soccer")
If they get in my way, I shoot them. If they die, well, they only have themselves to blame.
If they came here to steal from us. I'd be upset too. I'm still going to kill them, but I understand.
We take their radianite one way or another.

The nerve! They come here acting like they own the place. Cómo Pedro por su casa.
-# (cómo Pedro por su casa: "acting like they own the place")
You think they came here peacefully? No. Let that clear your conscience.
Ole! You hear the radio? If anyone finds it, change the station, my team is playing.
You want a fairy tale ending? They lost, end of story.

Qué nota. Now let's get something to eat.
-# (qué nota: "fantastic")
That's what following the rules get you.

Brimstone, mi hermano. No disagreements today, we have to show everyone how well we get along now.
-# (mi hermano: "my brother")
Let me take care of their Brimstone. It's therapy for me, don't ask why.
Clove, if you ever go freelance, do not mention the... Immortality. Your clients would take advantage, I certainly would.

Gekko, how about we keep the strategic comms to human languages today? No entiendo radivore.
-# (no entiendo radivore: "i don't understand")
Their Gekko's creatures will survive without him.
Iso, that is the work of a professional.

Señora Alves, don't get too eager out there with explosives, you'll put me out of a job.
-# (señora: "ms/mrs")

Señora Mondragón, me alegro de verle, I have a gift for the children of the sanctuary. Remind me after this.
-# (señora: "ms/mrs", me alegro de verle: "i'm glad to see you")
Time to kill the handsome colombian.
Seems like I'm the better one.
They brought the other me along, huh? I'm not supposed to be the target of these weapons.
Vyse, you are just as scary as you look.
You know, Vyse? You should lay flowers on the graves of your enemies. It's very poetic, and saves money on flowers.

Colgó los guayos.
-# ("hung up the cleats")
It was their life or mine.
And now they are all dead.
That's the job, get used to it.
I do prefer when they put up a fight.
Don't mess with an old soldier.
Do what you're here to do and we won't have a problem.
If they think it is more honorable to resist death, they're welcome to try.

My ballistic set up easy kills. And if they don't, pues... You can't complain if you're dead.
-# (pues: "well")
This should be simple enough, I flush them out, you finish them.
Remember, no one wants to die out here, but you don't always get what you want.
Killing them is easier than all these radianite business.

No den papaya. If you compromise your position, you hand them a free kill. Don't.
-# (no den papaya: "don't give them a chance")
We can stand around all day talking about killing them or we just... Do it.

Remember, I hit them with explosives then you go in. No la vayan a cagar.
-# (no la vayan a cagar: "don't screw it up")
Make peace with yourself before you pull the trigger, no one else can judge you.
Okay, now we do that some more.
If they don't like losing, they should do something about it.
Don't let a good fight go to your head. Sure is way to lose it.
You think they're worried? I think they're worried.
Nothing is guaranteed in war, but I like our odds.
I'm used to difficult work, this is not so difficult.

Keep pushing, tenemos mucho camello.
-# (tenemos mucho camello: "we have a lot of work")

Hey hermanos, spend everything you have.
-# (hermanos: "siblings")
You want to survive? Bring the right gun.
Now, they draw their very last breath.

Lo tenemos, hermanos.
-# ("we've got this, brothers")
There is no fight left in them now.
Whatever they get paid, it's too much.
So we move to plan D?
No excuses, get what we came for.
Don't they know stealing is wrong?
Our radianite is not theirs to take.
Back me into a corner? That's what happens.
Is this a joke to them?
Where I come from, we call that being resourceful.
You see? I can play by the book from time to time.
Did you think I'd let this thing go off?
Well, I lived a good life.
Not killing me was a mistake.

viper.text: No one can hold their breath forever.
They are not important. Let's move through them. Like smoke through lungs.
Only five of them? Pity, I brought enough poison for fifty. You can't say I'm not prepared.
Use my poison to your advantage. I don't deploy it for kicks.
I wonder if these ones would beg. They all do. After a while.
They call me a monster, shall I prove them right?
Bodies decompose after 12 hours in acid. There's no reason I know that.
Let's take from them what they took from me, everything.
I was saving my best poison for a special occasion, but our guests came all this way. It's the least I can do.
The lies we told this city, just to pry it open and suck it dry.
I knew some of them, the people here. Good scientists.
This dome won't protect the city forever, they wanna survive, stop hiding.
Hide the bodies, we weren't here.
I am your monster, you made me this way. Never forget that.
You were only in my way.
Well, the town is gone but our world stays afloat, I'll take that trade.
Well done, Breach. I knew hiring you was a good idea.
Do me a favor, Breach. And... Open them up. Toxin works best when directly injected.
Brimstone, we really need to put an age floor on VALORANT. I can't take this... Youth.
I'm impressed, Brimstone. Looks like the fire is still lit.
Don't tell me what to do, old man. Someone will die, no matter how fancy our strategy.
You want my approval, Chamber? Do that again.
You were charming, but not as clever as you think.
Chamber, you've made promises we expect you to keep. Less flirting, more focus. Thank you.
I look forward to watching the light leave their eyes.
Cypher, you collect information. Tell me, what are their dreams? What do they fear?
Tell me where they are, Cypher. I'll take care of the rest.
Their Cypher might find us, good. Bring them to me.
To be young and have reflexes again... Good work, Jett.
What a shame to take Jett's young life, truly a pity.
Something wrong, Kay/O? Deaths on your conscience? We're not so different after all.
You did well, little mouse. Keep it up.
Their Killjoy is too smart for her own good, I'll reprimand her.
Neon, what was that meal you made earlier? It was... Good.
Neon, you know I am supposed to be the scary one, right?
Neon, you can practice restraint later. You're at war now. I need the storm.
Ja- I mean, Omen. Keep yourself together, you're still needed.
Keep being their nightmare, old friend.
I wonder what's inside their Omen. What truth is he keeping from ours?
One more time, Omen. How many times have you heard that, now?
Fire needs oxygen. Let me replace this Phoenix's air.
Raze I will deny that I said this, but your inventions are... Valuable. Keep tinkering.
Eat your own heart out, Reyna.
Reyna, a woman after my own heart. You can't have it, though.
What's it like, Reyna? Fighting to keep a loved one alive. No, please. Tell me.
I respect the predation of their Reyna. It's almost inspiring.
Fill your heart, Reyna. If you want results, I need those souls.
Sage, you're the only one who can keep us alive. Don't fail us now like you failed me then.
Skye, you have no clue of the forces you are playing with. Don't worry, you'll be dead before you figure it out.
Guide us, Skye. Find your strength along the way.
Well done, Sova. You truly are a hunter.
You choked on your own poison. Tragic.
Sabine, Sabine, what have you been working on over there? I'm curious, but you don't need to be alive for me to find out.
Huh. My air filters don't work on her poison. Why? I'll figure it out.
You have the ability to riftwalk and you stay here? What a shame, there are so many better worlds out there.
You wanted to be a hero, didn't you?
Back where you belong, in the dirt.
This is everything I wanted. Wasn't it?
You wanted a villain? I gave you a villain!
Didn't need a gun for that one.
Remember, nobody's a hero when they're crying for air.
If any of you die, I lose a bet with Brimstone. So don't embarrass me like that please.
Look them in the eyes when you kill them.
They will die, hopeless and afraid.
If you lose focus, you die. Breathe when it's over.
Ah. This is what I live for.
Some vermin are born to die. Like rats in a lab.
Again. Don't stop. I want them in pieces.
Oh, if only I could always feel like this.
It's hard not to play with my food.
They had their fun. Now it's my turn.
Can't take anything with us after this. Go for broke.
We can't take anything with us after this.
They're in the coffin. Time to bury them.
One last push. Let's make them hurt.
We end them here, we end them forever.
I will not lose my home again!
They keep clawing our wall. Pathetic.
I want to see you crawl.
If you want something done right, do it yourself.
You only thought that was close.
I can't make this easier for them.
Should I use a stick next time?
Fascinating. I must record this feeling.
They think they can kill me?!

vyse.text: It's time. Remember your role. Keep your nerve. And if all else fails, send them my way.
Our enemies had every chance to back down. But they chose violence and I choose to reply in kind.
This is what we trained for. Pick a weapon, choose a sector and fight for your future.
I didn't come here to lose. We'll win or we'll die.
Practice is easy. Safe. Sterile. This is where you are truly measured.
History doesn't remember the almosts. We'll be the best or we'll be forgotten.
A battle is just a conflict in need of resolution. Focus on the fix, then execute.
Your enemy has everything you need to survive. You have the means to take it, so take it.
Five people stand between us and what's ours. Arm up and fight for your future.
Our key objectives today are, kill the opposition and plant the Spike. Great. Very doable.
The temerity. To think they can come here and take what's ours. No.
The self-righteous thieves are back. Good. I have plans for them.
If it were up to me, I'd have Raze rig this place with explosives and send it crashing into the void.
So this is the project that sapped my funding all those years ago? Looks like it worked out well for you Kingdom.
So much to research here... But here we are, about to fill it with bullet holes.
Hmm. Impressive engineering for a precarious little place.
Why hasn't Kingdom abandoned their headquarters here yet? Who would've thought? Huh? So be it.
Interverse research causing massive catastrophies. Huh. Imagine that.
That's one way of getting what you want, I suppose? I'll take it.
Victory might have been inevitable, but damn it feels good.
I deserve this. Uh. We. We deserve this.
I never thought I'd make pleasant memories here. Huh. Well done.
You're a disruptive one, Breach. But that's welcomed here. Go rattle their heads for us.
Say you hadn't founded VALORANT, Brimstone. Do you think you'd still get in now? Do you think you have something the rest of us don't, besides from experience of course.
Their Brimstone will learn what real leadership looks like.
Oh good, they brought the gun obsessed valet. Let's see if his predictability matches his vanity.
I can't end their Clove but I can break their spirit.
Their Cypher will share his knowledge with me. Even if I have to prise it out of him.
You remind me of me sometimes, Fade. Good work.
I hear Fade has trouble sleeping. Hm. I'll be her remedy.
That's one way of manifesting flow state, nicely done, Iso.
I studied robotics for a time. But I've never seen anything like you, Kay/O. Remarkable.
Whoever puts their Kay/O back together is going to have their hands full after this.
They call their Killjoy a genius and yet here she is, walking into a battlefield wearing bright yellow.
Omen, the Scions spoke of you often. Is it true you once killed a man with a tree branch?
I never tire of watching you work, Omen.
Omen, surely VALORANT has the budget to replace those rags hanging off you.
This isn't fair, being forced to fight Omen. But this isn't a fair world.
So... You use explosives to propel yourself, Raze. That's... That's creative. I think I like it.
Tactically sound, practically proficient. Fine work, Reyna.
I'll give their Sage something to heal.
We saved the world once, Sabine. I don't doubt that we can do it again.
Oh Sabine, how did we both change careers and still end up working together?
Who do you think you are?
I see I have an imposter across the way. Hm. I'll take it as a compliment.
I want Yoru's head. Figuratively. But also let's kill him.
If you can't do something right, don't do it at all.
You can't see my face right now, but just know, I'm smiling.
And you were doing so well...
Who gave you all that confidence?
If any of you mattered, you'd be alive.
This world will be one that I make.
I have the vision. I am the means.
I'll drive this world forward by my damn self.
I'm a hands-on kind of leader.
You have to break some bones to change the world.
They brought weapons made of metal? To kill me? Huh. Ironic.
Control the space, control their choices.
Speak up and ask questions. Assumptions will only get us in trouble.
I feel no empathy for them. What does that say about me? Don't answer. It was rhetorical.
Ability, dedication, time. That's all we need.
I'll isolate the problem. You crush it.
This is where someone says something pithy and we pretend to tolerate them. Go ahead, I'll wait.
Keep pushing don't give them time to adapt.
Hm. I'm partial to winning, let's do more of it.
Success is the only axis that matters.
People are all the same. Predictable. Punishable.
I love it when our competition embraces chaos theory and makes the same mistakes expecting different results.
There's something to be said for down right doggedness. Most people would know when they're beaten.
Never interrupt your enemy when they're making a mistake.
If they're learning it's not fast enough.
Good. Now we build on this success.
Momentum is a powerful thing. Keep it up.
That was evidence of our worth, now we prove it.
Frugality has its place, but it's not here. Spend.
No sense in saving now. Spend. Enjoy the arsenal.
Mercy now would be weakness. Break them.
Their spirits are broken, let's attend to the rest.
Alright then, let's go kill them.
You get what you fight for.
I am the master of my fate.
What are the use in lessons if we don't learn?
This world will know my name!
I am everything that you're not.
I expected a little more competency.
A team like this can do anything.
Good this is our new standard.
That's a hell of a benchmark.
All that and with so few means.
You have to be smarter than that.
Can't die yet. So much... To do.

waylay.text: I don't try, I do.
Remember if I spot any of you being stupid out there, I will kick your ass when we get back. And I kick hard.
Practice doesn't perfect, it makes better. It means we're going in today the best we've ever been.
Another day in paradise! I love this job.

No need to worry, my หมอดู predicted a big win in my life today. Which is a nice way of saying our enemies are screwed.
-# (หมอดู: "fortune teller")

I could have sworn we were about to fight, but you fools all look ready for nap time. Be tired later, yeah? ไป!
-# (ไป: "go")

โชคดีทุกคน! Means good luck, more or less. Not that we need it.
-# (โชคดีทุกคน: "good luck everyone")
Momentum and pressure, yeah? That's all we need to crack this place open.
Looks like a smash and grab gig. Hm. Just like old times.
Seems that we've got visitors. I'll run point on our little welcoming committee. Unless any of you feel up for the challenge.

อุ๊ย! Another incursion? I'm all for making bad decisions, but at some point they've got to learn... no?
-# อุ๊ย: "ouch")
This team is shaping up into something special. Do you know that?
You'll give my team their damn respect!
Man! I love you guys. So goddamn proud.
That's right! WE. DON'T. PLAY.
Alright, looks like their other us brought their A-team. So, no dumbass plays today, okay? I am NOT NOT talking to you, Breach.
Breach, shame we never got to work together before all this, ey? The jobs we could have done.
Looking to you, Brimstone.

ให้ได้อย่างงี้เซ่, Brimstone! I'll just send everybody else home now.
-# (ให้ได้อย่างงี้เซ่: "that's how it's done")
Alright! We've got Brimstone riding shotgun today. Who wants to show him what we've been working on?
Hey, Brim, need a minute after this. Got an idea for something we can work on back at base.
Jett, you and me.
That's what I'm talking about, Jett! Proud of you.
Sorry little wind.
Jett, Jett, Jett. You should know better.

เฮ้ย, Jett! Little wind and I fighting side by side. Love that for us, hate that for them.
-# (เฮ้ย: "hey")
Their Jett wouldn't know experience if it shot her between the eyes, which, it might.
Gonna have to teach their Omen that there is nothing brave about hiding in the shadows.
That's leadership, Phoenix. That's quality, so good!
Raze, you're up.
Oh-oh, Raze! 10 out of 10 for results, lady! And 0 for subtlety.
Show me what you got, Sage.
Uh. Hi there, Battle Sage. Nice to meet you! Don't let me get in your way.
Their Sage is good but she is so stiff. I just wanna go over there and shake some fun into that girl.
You spot them Sova and I'll kill them.
Their Tejo is not my Tejo.

Still got it, T! เจ๋งว่ะ!
-# (เจ๋งว่ะ: "that's dope")

Adios, T.
-# (adios: "bye")
You taught a shark to swim, T.
If their Tejo thinks his little rockets can make me move, he is... Probably right.
Their Vyse is one kind of smart, I'm the other.
There's only one me.

ได้อยู่ได้อยู่!
-# ("still got it, still got it")

คิดว่าแน่นักหรอ.
-# ("do you really think you're that good?")
Uh. They brought me? Well, you gotta be the best some time.
Eyes on Yoru.

มีเก่งกว่านี้ป่ะ?
-# ("is there anyone better than this?")

โดนไปดิ!
-# ("take that")

สมน้ำหน้า!
-# ("serves you right")
There's that.
Next!
Too bad.
You're done!
Yep!
Too slow!
Uh-huh.

อุ๊ย!
-# ("ouch")

เชดดดดดด!
-# ("shit")

สุดยอด.
-# ("superb")

เริ่ด!
-# ("amazing")

ปั้งๆ!
-# ("bang bang")
Oooh!
Nailed!
I'm good!
Stay dead!
Yah! Stupid should hurt!
That's a dumb way to die.
Didn't wanna join your friends, huh?
How did you think that was gonna end?
Not so fancy now, huh?
Got three!
Four!
Shhh. The kids are sleeping!
Rest of you get that down? Need me to do it again?
Sorry, I couldn't help myself.
There's 5 reasons!
Knock-out!
That's a beatdown.
Ugh! That sounded nasty.

ทุกคนโอเคนะ? You all feeling good? We got this!
-# (ทุกคนโอเคนะ: "everybody okay?")
Everyone good? Take a sec if you need.
Take a minute, focus on your breathing, helps with your aim.
No one's gonna give you what you want. Work for it.
We show up now, we live later.
Getting tired is optional, keep the energy up!
Hey, hey! Stay focused! Those shits are trying to kill us!
You know the drill, gear up and get back out there. I don't want any sass about it.
Everyone having fun? If you're not, you're in the wrong line of work.
I know I give you guys a hard time. But you're better off with me kicking your butt than those assholes shooting at you.

โอ๊ย อ่อนโว้ย! They're just realising they walked into the wrong end of the shooting range! Anyone need ammo?
-# (โอ๊ย อ่อนโว้ย: "oh man, so pathetic")
We are working now! What else they got, huh?
